SHG Installation
****************

Prerequisites
-------------

Development environment is Linux debian 3.16.0-4-amd64 (Debian
Jessie). Additionaly, GCC 5.4.0 or Clang 3.8.0, FFTW and GSL libraries
and doxygen 1.8.11 are required for compilation and generating
documentation. To compile some inessential auxiliary programs, Intel
Math Kernel Library 11.1.2, GNU Multiple Precision Arithmetic Library
6.0.0a and Numerical Recipes Third Edition (version 3.02) are
required.

Compilation and testing
-----------------------

Change directory to the main directory of the project. To build the
library, say make lib. To compile the testing program, say make
testing. To run the tests, say make check.

Documentation
-------------

To generate documentation, say make doc. The HTML documentation is
generated in doc/html directory.

Installation
------------

To install the library in /usr/local, say make install. To change the
installation directory, change the prefix variable near the top of
Makefile.
